{"tid":1140952,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國宣布派航母及轟炸機往中東威懾伊朗","createTime":"2019-05-06T07:10:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T07:33:31.000Z","uid":28765,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e5a4a2b003e1e419ef6dac8d1a814411d0652add","tid":1140952,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T07:10:13.000Z","msg":"2019/5/6<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190506/s00005/7116c54d96b7cc3110f11adfa6c80797.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190506%2Fs00005%2F7116c54d96b7cc3110f11adfa6c80797.jpg&h=a3419e3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國與伊朗的關係進一步緊張，美國國家安全顧問博爾頓周日（5日）宣布，華府正派遣「林肯」號航空母艦戰鬥群和轟炸機特遣部隊前往中東，是向伊朗發出清晰信息，警告伊朗若對美國或盟友利益發動攻擊，將遭到「無情的打擊」。<br />\n<br />\n博爾頓發聲明說：「為回應連串令人不安及升級的迹象和警告，美國正向美軍中央司令部地區，部署『林肯』號航母戰鬥群和一支轟炸機特遣部隊，藉以向伊朗政權發出清楚及無誤的信息，即任何對美國或我們盟友利益的攻擊，都將遭到無情打擊。」博爾頓稱，美國不尋求與伊朗開戰，但已做好充分準備，回應任何攻擊，無論是伊朗通過的代理人、伊斯蘭革命衛隊或伊朗常規部隊。<br />\n<br />\n路透社引述一名美國官員說：「這些（美軍）部隊已被下令進入中東地區，藉此威懾伊朗部隊的潛在準備工作，這可能表明該地區可能會襲擊美軍。」<br />\n<br />\n特朗普政府日前已停止對任何伊朗石油進口國給予豁免，希望將伊朗石油出口量降至零，並將伊朗的伊斯蘭革命衛隊列為恐怖組織。<br />\n<br />\n（衛報/路透社）<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20190506/s00005/1557116068846/美宣布派航母及轟炸機往中東威懾伊朗\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20190506%2Fs00005%2F1557116068846%2F%E7%BE%8E%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E6%B4%BE%E8%88%AA%E6%AF%8D%E5%8F%8A%E8%BD%9F%E7%82%B8%E6%A9%9F%E5%BE%80%E4%B8%AD%E6%9D%B1%E5%A8%81%E6%87%BE%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97&d=JxdAuiyzJYRXF2tJvMOkN0kSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=dbfacd12\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20190506%2Fs00005%2F1557116068846%2F%E7%BE%8E%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E6%B4%BE%E8%88%AA%E6%AF%8D%E5%8F%8A%E8%BD%9F%E7%82%B8%E6%A9%9F%E5%BE%80%E4%B8%AD%E6%9D%B1%E5%A8%81%E6%87%BE%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97&h=d3e8fecd\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20190506/s00005/1557116068846/美宣布派航母及轟炸機往中東威懾伊朗</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國佬又表演一個打九個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d2270faa74c243d5ad1f292cff602e5fe9a9164","tid":1140952,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T07:12:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2c480fe5c8e7acb3a17ce5de8f0ba7a57d1b3dcf","tid":1140952,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T07:13:03.000Z","msg":"伊朗咪又係支那隻狗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa06f47d9b27bfcd657eeb8e9c98714fc84a973d","tid":1140952,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T07:16:12.000Z","msg":"幾時過黎香港走轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e20b1957ffad4808f329c4f03421b74e07c584d","tid":1140952,"uid":18955,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"aa06f47d9b27bfcd657eeb8e9c98714fc84a973d","tid":1140952,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T07:16:12.000Z","msg":"幾時過黎香港走轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T07:33:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}